dc_description_s: This ESRI Geodatabase contains polygon features and attribute data tables for census data for the country of Costa Rica. The data is derived from INEC CostaRica (Instituto Nactional de Estadisticas y Censos) and was released in 2011. The data contain 473 census boundary polygons that each have 155 attributes, and the lowest administrative boundary level represented is Distritos. Refer to the documentation for a list of variables and a translation of variable titles into English. For more information on the census methodology and a glossary of variable categories, go to the INEC website at http://www.inec.go.cr/.
